{
  "stem": "19502.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was hanging on to my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Apparently, he wanted to spite me, so he grabbed me so hard by the hand, he just gave me like a throw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Come.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And took.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he took me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the last I saw my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took us in a place where we're sitting-- women were sitting, and then on the other side, I give a look.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My brother is between the-- the men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the meantime, we hear noises.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like, you could hear shooting, bang, bang, bang, bang, bang.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know I mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could hear it all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in front, by this side, as we were sitting on-- on one-- this one-- Benches?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No benches.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the ground we were sitting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Benches, that would have been a luxury.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They sat us on the ground, but in a-- in a yard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somebody else's-- [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Klener's ?] yard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Klener's ?] yard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then as-- and in the back, we turned around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In our town we had [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Razel. ?] Three-- two sisters and a mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A whole year they were fine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It came summertime, spring, they-- they were mentally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Razel ?] had a baby, a-- a-- you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they made her-- they made her dance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they made her sing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was singing heil Hitler, live Hitler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They made her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they grabbed that child from her, and down there was a fence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took the child and they smashed it against the fence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, we were all stunned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, there's no tears.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's-- and-- you know, you-- you just go to-- you-- you-- there's only a will to survive somehow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's-- you have no feelings anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
